function sysCall_init()
-- This is executed exactly once, the first time this script is executed trubbleBubbleBase=sim.getObjectHandle(sim.handle_self) -- this is bubbleRob's handle leftMotor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_leftMotor") -- Handle of the left motor rightMotor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_rightMotor") -- Handle of the right motor obstacleSensor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_obstacleSensor") -- Obstacle sensor barrierSensor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_barrierSensor_vision") -- Barrier sensor heatSensor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_heat_sensor") -- Heat sensor personSensor=sim.getObjectHandle("trubbleBubble_person_sensor") -- Person sensor minMaxSpeed={50*math.pi/180,600*math.pi/180} -- Min and max speeds for each motor backUntilTime=-1 -- Controls forward / reverse motion of trubbleBubble collisionAvoidanceUntilTime=-1 -- Controls collision avoidance measures for trubbleBubble fireAvoidanceUntilTime=-1 -- Controls fire avoidance measures of trubbleBubble robotCollection=sim.createCollection(0) sim.addItemToCollection(robotCollection,sim.handle_tree,trubbleBubbleBase,0) distanceSegment=sim.addDrawingObject(sim.drawing_lines,4,0,-1,1,{0,1,0}) robotTrace=sim.addDrawingObject(sim.drawing_linestrip+sim.drawing_cyclic,2,0,-1,200,{1,1,0},nil,nil,{1,1,0}) clearanceGraph=sim.getObjectHandle('trubbleBubble_clearance') distStream=sim.addGraphStream(clearanceGraph,'Trubble Bubble Clearance','m',0,{1,0,0}) -- Create the custom UI: xml = '<ui title="'..sim.getObjectName(trubbleBubbleBase)..' speed" closeable="false" resizeable="false" activate="false">'..[[ <hslider minimum="0" maximum="100" on-change="speedChange_callback" id="1"/> <label text="" style="* {margin-left: 300px;}"/> </ui> ]] ui=simUI.create(xml) speed=(minMaxSpeed[1]+minMaxSpeed[2])*0.5 simUI.setSliderValue(ui,1,100*(speed-minMaxSpeed[1])/(minMaxSpeed[2]-minMaxSpeed[1]))
end
-- Sensing Functions -- function sysCall_sensing() local result,distData=sim.checkDistance(robotCollection,sim.handle_all) if result>0 then sim.addDrawingObjectItem(distanceSegment,nil) sim.addDrawingObjectItem(distanceSegment,distData) sim.setGraphStreamValue(clearanceGraph,distStream,distData[7]) end local p=sim.getObjectPosition(trubbleBubbleBase,-1) sim.addDrawingObjectItem(robotTrace,p) end
function speedChange_callback(ui,id,newVal) speed=minMaxSpeed[1]+(minMaxSpeed[2]-minMaxSpeed[1])*newVal/100 end
-- Sensor Functions -- function sysCall_actuation()
-- Barrier Sensing -- barrier=sim.getVisionSensorCharImage(barrierSensor) -- Read the barrier sensor
-- Get RGB color pixel values from reading and assign to variables redPixel=barrier:byte(1) greenPixel=barrier:byte(2) bluePixel=barrier:byte(3)
-- Set bot in collision avoidance mode if barrier is encountered if(bluePixel>150) then collisionAvoidanceUntilTime=sim.getSimulationTime()+0.75 end
-- Obstacle Sensing -- obstacle=sim.readProximitySensor(obstacleSensor) -- Read the obstacle sensor
-- If a near obstacle is detected, set trubbleBubble in backup mode if(obstacle>0) then backUntilTime=sim.getSimulationTime()+4 end
-- Fire Sensing -- fire=sim.readProximitySensor(heatSensor) -- Read the fire sensor
-- If fire is detected, if(fire>0) then fireAvoidanceUntilTime=sim.getSimulationTime()+1 end
-- Person Sensing -- person=sim.readProximitySensor(personSensor) -- Read person sensor
-- If person is detected if(person>0) then print("ALERT! ALERT! TRAPPED PERSON DETECTED WHO IS IN NEED OF IMMEDIATE MEDICAL ATTENTION") end
-- Control of trubbleBubble movement modes if (backUntilTime<sim.getSimulationTime() and collisionAvoidanceUntilTime<sim.getSimulationTime() and fireAvoidanceUntilTime<sim.getSimulationTime()) then -- Setting wheel motor speeds for normal forward mode sim.setJointTargetVelocity(leftMotor,speed) sim.setJointTargetVelocity(rightMotor,speed) elseif(backUntilTime>sim.getSimulationTime()) then -- Setting the wheel motor speeds for obstacle avoidance mode sim.setJointTargetVelocity(leftMotor,-speed/2) sim.setJointTargetVelocity(rightMotor,-speed/8) elseif(collisionAvoidanceUntilTime>sim.getSimulationTime()) then -- Setting the wheel motor speeds for barrier avoidance mode sim.setJointTargetVelocity(leftMotor,-speed/2) sim.setJointTargetVelocity(rightMotor,0) elseif(fireAvoidanceUntilTime>sim.getSimulationTime()) then -- Setting the wheel motor speeds for barrier avoidance mode print("EXCESSIVE HEAT DETECTED -- INITIATING EVASIVE MANEUVEERS") sim.setJointTargetVelocity(leftMotor,-speed/2) sim.setJointTargetVelocity(rightMotor,0) end
-- Control of trubbleBubble if it gets stuck while(clearanceGraph == 0) do sim.setJointTargetVelocity(leftMotor, -speed) sim.setJointTargetVelocity(rightMotor, -speed) end end
function sysCall_cleanup() simUI.destroy(ui) end
